motorbit.MotorRunDelay|param|delay: number second delay to stop; eg: 1
motorbit.MotorRunDelay|param|index: number Motor Index; eg: A01A02, B01B02, A03A04, B03B04
motorbit.MotorRunDual: Execute two motors at the same time

motorbit.MotorRunDualDelay|param|motor1: number First Motor; eg: A01A02, B01B02
motorbit.MotorRunDualDelay|param|motor2: number Second Motor; eg: A03A04, B03B04
motorbit.MotorRunDual|param|motor1: number First Motor; eg: A01A02, B01B02
motorbit.MotorRunDual|param|motor2: number Second Motor; eg: A03A04, B03B04
motorbit.StpCarMove|param|diameter: number diameter of wheel in mm; eg: 48
motorbit.StpCarMove|param|distance: number Distance to move in cm; eg: 10, 20
motorbit.StpCarTurn|param|diameter: number diameter of wheel in mm; eg: 48
motorbit.StpCarTurn|param|track: number track width of car; eg: 125
